<br>
    So far multiplayer mods have been very boring. The servers geared towards pvp always have people on them that created armor/weapons for themselves so they are invincible and do crazy damage making it pointless, and the regular mods out so far that I've seen are all pretty lame. When better mods are made, it might be fun again.<br>
